definitions.definition: A city , the county seat of Sheboygan County , Wisconsin , United States .
A town in Sheboygan County , Wisconsin , United States , adjacent to the city of the same name.
A river in Wisconsin , United States , which runs into Lake Michigan at Sheboygan; in full, Sheboygan River .
